generic:link.msg:message: Identity " Value of 'Capital ' ( = Equity + Perpetual preference shares + Non-perpetual preference shares + Others (Please furnish, if any) )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Reserves & surplus' ( = Share Premium Account + General Reserves + Statutory/Special Reserve (Section 45-IC reserve to be shown separately below item no.(vii)) + Reserves under Sec 45-IC of RBI Act 1934 + Capital Redemption Reserve + Debenture Redemption Reserve + Other Capital Reserves + Other Revenue Reserves + Investment Fluctuation Reserves/ Investment Reserves + Revaluation Reserves + Share Application Money Pending Allotment + Others (Please mention) + Balance of profit and loss account) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Revaluation Reserves' ( = Revl. Reserves - Property + Revl. Reserves - Financial Assets )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Bonds & Notes' ( = Fixed rate plain vanilla including zero coupons + Instruments with embedded options + Floating rate instruments )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Borrowings' ( = Bank borrowings + Inter Corporate Debts (other than related parties) + Loan from Related Parties (including ICDs) + Corporate Debts + Commercial Papers + Non - Convertible Debentures (NCDs) (A+B) + Convertible Debentures (A+B) + Subordinate Debt + Perpetual Debt Instrument + Borrowings From Central Government / State Government + Borrowings From Public Sector Undertakings (PSUs) + Other Borrowings )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Bank borrowings' ( = Bank Borrowings in the nature ofTerm money borrowings + Bank Borrowings in the nature of WCDL + Bank Borrowings in the nature of Cash Credits (CC) + Bank Borrowings in the nature of Letter of Credits(LCs) + Bank Borrowings in the nature ofECBs )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Total Borrowings ' ( = Fixed Rate Borrowings + Floating Rate Borrowings )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Commercial Papers ' ( = Subscribed by Mutual Funds + Subscribed by Banks + Subscribed by NBFCs + Subscribed by Insurance Companies + Subscribed by Pension Funds Subscribed by Retail Investors + Others (Please specify) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Total Debentures' ( = sum of values of all counter parties )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Current Liabilities & Provisions' ( = Sundry creditors + Expenses payable + Advance income received from borrowers pending adjustment + Interest payable on deposits and borrowings + Provisions for Standard Assets + Provisions for NPAs + Provisions for Investment Portfolio (NPI) + Other Provisions (Please Specify) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Unclamed Deposits' ( = Pending for less than 7 years + Pending for greater than 7 years )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Total OUTFLOWS' ( = Capital + Reserves & surplus + Gifts, grants, donations & benefactions + Bonds & Notes + Deposits + Borrowings + Current Liabilities & Provisions + Repos / Bills Rediscounted + Statutory Dues + Unclamed Deposits + Any other Unclaimed Amount + Debt Service Realisation Account + Others + Total Outflows account of OBS items (OO) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Balances with Banks' ( = Current account + In deposit accounts, and other placements + Money at Call & Short Notice )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Investments (net of provisions)' ( = Fixed Income Securities + Floating rate securities + Equity Shares + Convertible Preference Shares + In shares of Subsidiaries / Joint Ventures + In shares of Venture Capital Funds + Others )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Fixed Income Securities' ( = Government Securities + Zero Coupon Bonds + Bonds + Debentures + Cumulative Redeemable Preference Shares + Non-Cumulative Redeemable Preference Shares + Others (Please Specify) )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Floating Rate Securities' ( = Government Securities + Zero Coupon Bonds + Bonds + Debentures + Cumulative Redeemable Preference Shares + Non-Cumulative Redeemable Preference Shares + Others (Please Specify) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Advances (Performing)' ( = Bills of exchange and promissory notes discounted & rediscounted + Term loans + Corporate loans/short term loans )" do not tally
Identity " Value of Total of 'Term Loan' or 'Corporate loans/short term loans' ( = Fixed Rate + Floating Rate )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Non-Performing Loans' ( = Sub-standard Category + Doubtful Category + Loss Category )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Other Assets' ( = Intangible assets & other non-cash flow items + Other items (e.g. accrued income, other receivables, staff loans, etc.) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Unclamed Deposits' ( = Pending for less than 7 years + Pending for greater than 7 years )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'TOTAL INFLOWS ' ( = Cash + Remittance in transit + Balances with Banks + Investments (net of provisions) + Advances (Performing) + Non-Performing Loans + Assets on Lease + Fixed assets (excluding assets on lease) + Other Assets + Statutory Dues + Unclamed Deposits + Any other Unclaimed Amount + Debt Service Realisation Account + Total Inflow account of OBS items (OI) )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Mismatch(B - A)' ( = TOTAL INFLOWS - Total OUTFLOWS )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Mismatch as % of Total Outflows' ( = Mismatch (B - A) / Total OUTFLOWS )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for the period of 0 to 7 Days ( ='Mismatch' for the same period )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for 8 day to 14 days ( = 'Mismatch' for 8 day to 14 days + Cumulative mismatch for 0 day to 7 days )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for 15 days to 30/31 days (One month) ( = 'Mismatch' for 15 days to 30/31 days (One month) + Cumulative mismatch for 8 day to 14 days )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over one month and upto 2 months ( = 'Mismatch' for Over one month and upto 2 months + Cumulative mismatch for 15 days to 30/31 days (One month) )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over two months and upto 3 months ( = 'Mismatch'for Over two months and upto 3 months + Cumulative mismatch for Over one month and upto 2 months)" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 3 months and upto 6 months ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 3 months and upto 6 months + Cumulative mismatch for Over two months and upto 3 months )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 6 months and upto 1 year ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 6 months and upto 1 year plus Cumulative mismatch for Over 3 months and upto 6 months )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 1 year and upto 3 years ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 1 year and upto 3 years + 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 6 months and upto 1 year )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 3 years and upto 5 years ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 3 years and upto 5 years + Cumulative mismatch for Over 1 year and upto 3 years)" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 5 years ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 5 years + Cumulative mismatch for Over 3 years and upto 5 years )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Non-sensitive ( = 'Mismatch' for Over 5 years + 'Cumulative mismatch' for Over 5 years )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative mismatch' for Total ( = Cumulative mismatch for Non-sensitive)" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Deposits' ( = Term Deposits/ Fixed Deposits from public )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Term Deposits/ Fixed Deposits from public' ( = Fixed rate plus + Floating rate )" do not tally

Identity " Value of 'Total' ( = (0 to 7 days + 8 day to 14 days + 15 days to 30/31 days (One month) + Over one month and upto 2 months + Over two months and upto 3 months + Over 3 months and upto 6 months + Over 6 months and upto 1 year + Over 1 year and upto 3 years + Over 3 years and upto 5 years + Over 5 years + Non-sensitive )" do not tally
Identity " Value of 'Cumulative Mismatch as % of Cumulative Total Outflows' ( = 'Cumulative Mismatch' / 'A1. Cumulative Outflows')" do not tally

"If ""Cumulative Mismatch"" is positive then ""Cumulative Mismatch as % of Cumulative Total Outflows"" should be positive. If ""Cumulative Mismatch"" is negative then ""Cumulative Mismatch as % of Cumulative Total Outflows"" should be negative."
"If ""Mismatch (B - A)"" is positive then ""Mismatch as % of Total Outflows"" should be positive. If ""Mismatch (B - A)"" is positive then ""Mismatch as % of Total Outflows"" should be positive."
